        "created_at": "2019-01-06T03:47:04.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Evening,</p>\n<p>Wondering if anyone would be able to provide a (high level) comparison of some of the coche dury reds. Looking for general info on the wines as a whole as opposed to a specific vintage comparison.</p>\n<p>Auxey Duresse vs Mersault Rouge vs Volnay</p>\n<p>Any info would be appreciated. If there\u2019s a thread that covers this please also let me know.</p>\n<p>Cheers.</p>\n<p>Lucas</p>",
        "post_number": 1,
        "post_type": 1,
        "posts_count": 13,
        "updated_at": "2022-06-03T08:22:37.670Z",
