        "created_at": "2019-01-06T10:46:11.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>The Meursault Rouge is more chunky / rustic with the Auxey-Duresses in the same register but a bit finer boned; whereas the Volnay wines are more supple and elegant. So pretty much different as you would expect.</p>",
