        "created_at": "2019-01-07T20:17:59.000Z",
        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group quote-modified\" data-post=\"8\" data-topic=\"148686\">\n<blockquote>\n<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-post=\"5\" data-topic=\"148686\">\n<blockquote>\n<p>Better be good Bourgogne at 200 a pop</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>I opened a 2010 bourgogne from them two weeks ago and i really disliked it. I think their wines have an odd artificial sweetness to them.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>They\u2019re pandering to the Canadian market.</p>",
