        "created_at": "2019-01-07T20:38:13.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Must be all that icewine we drink up here that makes 'em so attractive to us.   <img src=\"/uploads/db3686/original/2X/3/3bd35321ffd7ed2243d1d518ebb606d554360600.gif\" width=\"50\" height=\"22\" alt=\"neener\" title=\"[neener.gif]\"></p>\n<p>Sorry\u2013I stand by my note.  And IIRC, I think I picked that up for USD $95 or so in Detroit a couple years ago.</p>",
